<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Property Operations · Discovery</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&family=Inter+Tight:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --sand: #f4ede1;
    --sand-deep: #e8dcc7;
    --paper: #fbf7ef;
    --ink: #0e2a37;
    --ink-soft: #2b4757;
    --muted: #7a8a93;
    --ocean: #1a5878;
    --ocean-light: #3a7a9a;
    --sun: #d97a3c;
    --sun-soft: #e8a878;
    --seafoam: #9cc4c4;
    --line: #d7cdb9;
    --line-soft: #e5dcc8;
    --highlight: #fde8b8;
    --shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(14,42,55,0.04), 0 8px 24px -12px rgba(14,42,55,0.12);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--sand);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: "Inter Tight", -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-feature-settings: "ss01", "cv11";
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  body {
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(26, 88, 120, 0.08), transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 100% 100%, rgba(217, 122, 60, 0.06), transparent 70%);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .grain {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.4; z-index: 1;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='2'/%3E%3CfeColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.05 0 0 0 0 0.16 0 0 0 0 0.21 0 0 0 0.08 0'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 32px 120px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* Header */
  header { margin-bottom: 40px; padding-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); position: relative; }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: "Inter Tight", sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ocean); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before { content: ""; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--ocean); }

  h1 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif; font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 20px; color: var(--ink);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ocean); font-weight: 300; }

  .lede { font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.55; }

  /* Sticky control bar */
  .control-bar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 12px;
    z-index: 10;
    margin: 32px 0 40px;
    background: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.92);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .search-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--sand);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .search-wrap:focus-within {
    background: white;
    border-color: var(--ocean);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26, 88, 120, 0.12);
  }
  .search-wrap svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .search-input {
    flex: 1;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    background: transparent;
    font-family: "Inter Tight", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .search-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }

  .search-clear {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--line); color: var(--ink-soft);
    border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px;
    display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    line-height: 1; padding: 0;
  }
  .search-wrap.has-value .search-clear { display: flex; }
  .search-clear:hover { background: var(--ink); color: white; }

  .progress-block {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    padding-right: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .progress-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }
  .progress-text strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .progress-bar {
    width: 100px; height: 6px; background: var(--sand-deep);
    border-radius: 100px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ocean), var(--seafoam));
    border-radius: 100px; width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .control-actions { display: flex; gap: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .btn {
    font-family: "Inter Tight", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 9px 16px; border-radius: 100px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--ocean); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--sand-deep); color: var(--ink); }

  /* Section card */
  .section-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .section-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .section-card.hidden { display: none; }

  .section-header {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    user-select: none;
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }
  .section-header:hover { background: rgba(232, 220, 199, 0.3); }

  .section-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sand-deep);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ocean); font-style: italic;
  }
  .section-card.theme-property .section-marker { background: var(--sand-deep); }
  .section-card.theme-cross .section-marker { background: var(--ink); color: var(--sun-soft); }
  .section-card.theme-ops .section-marker { background: #d8e4eb; color: var(--ocean); }
  .section-card.theme-systems .section-marker { background: #e0e9d8; color: #4a6b3a; }
  .section-card.theme-stay .section-marker { background: #f0d9c4; color: #8a4a1f; }
  .section-card.theme-protocol .section-marker { background: #e4d4e0; color: #6b3a5a; }
  .section-card.theme-standard .section-marker { background: var(--seafoam); color: var(--ink); }
  .section-card.theme-cameras .section-marker { background: #2b4757; color: var(--sun-soft); }
  .section-card.theme-logins .section-marker { background: #f0e4b4; color: #6b5a1a; }
  .section-card.theme-journeys .section-marker { background: #d9c4e4; color: #4a3a6b; }
  .section-card.theme-compliance .section-marker { background: #e4c4c4; color: #8a3a3a; }

  .section-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .section-meta {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted);
  }
  .meta-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .meta-pill .dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--seafoam);
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .meta-pill.complete .dot { background: var(--sun); }

  .toggle-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; transition: all 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .section-card.expanded .toggle-icon {
    background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); transform: rotate(180deg);
  }
  .toggle-icon svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; color: var(--ink); transition: color 0.2s ease; }
  .section-card.expanded .toggle-icon svg { color: var(--paper); }

  .section-body {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  .section-card.expanded .section-body { max-height: 20000px; }

  .section-body-inner {
    padding: 0 28px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }

  /* Question rows */
  .question-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .question-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .question-row.answered .question-text { color: var(--muted); }
  .question-row.hidden { display: none; }

  .checkbox-wrap { flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 2px; }
  .checkbox {
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .checkbox:hover { border-color: var(--ocean); }
  .checkbox.checked { background: var(--ocean); border-color: var(--ocean); }
  .checkbox svg {
    width: 14px; height: 14px; color: white;
    opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5);
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .checkbox.checked svg { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }

  .question-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .question-id {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ocean); font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .question-text {
    font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .question-text mark {
    background: var(--highlight);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 1px 2px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .answer-input {
    width: 100%; min-height: 0;
    padding: 0; border: none;
    background: transparent;
    font-family: "Inter Tight", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    resize: none; overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    max-height: 0; opacity: 0;
  }
  .question-row.show-input .answer-input {
    max-height: 400px; opacity: 1;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: var(--sand);
    border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }
  .answer-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--ocean);
    background: white;
  }
  .answer-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }

  /* Empty state */
  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: none;
  }
  .empty-state.show { display: block; }
  .empty-state h3 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  /* Summary card */
  .summary-card {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding: 40px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    border-radius: 16px;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 0% 0%, rgba(26, 88, 120, 0.6), transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 100% 100%, rgba(217, 122, 60, 0.2), transparent 70%);
  }
  .summary-card h2 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .summary-card h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sun-soft); }
  .summary-card p { color: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.7); margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 14px; }

  .summary-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .stat {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.06);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.08);
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1; color: var(--sun-soft);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.5); margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .summary-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-light { background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); }
  .btn-light:hover { background: var(--sand); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent; color: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.25);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--paper); background: rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.05);
  }

  .wave-divider {
    text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 32px;
    color: var(--line);
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 1.5em;
  }

  .toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(140%);
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(14,42,55,0.4);
    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .toast.show { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .container { padding: 32px 20px 80px; }
    .control-bar { flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 12px; }
    .search-wrap { width: 100%; order: -1; }
    .progress-block { flex: 1; }
    .section-header { padding: 18px 18px; gap: 14px; }
    .section-body-inner { padding: 0 18px 20px; }
    .section-marker { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 14px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 18px; }
    .summary-card { padding: 28px 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 38px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="grain"></div>

<div class="container">
  <header>
    <div class="eyebrow">Operations Discovery · 30A Portfolio</div>
    <h1>The <em>complete</em><br>operations workbook.</h1>
    <p class="lede">A single working document covering property-level questions, operational controls, guest issue protocols, journey messaging, and compliance. Search to filter on the fly, check off each item as it's resolved, and capture decisions inline.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="control-bar">
    <div class="search-wrap" id="search-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
        <line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"></line>
      </svg>
      <input type="text" id="search" class="search-input" placeholder="Filter questions, IDs, or sections…" />
      <button class="search-clear" id="search-clear" aria-label="Clear search">✕</button>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-block">
      <div class="progress-text"><strong id="answered-count">0</strong> / <span id="total-count">0</span></div>
      <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="expandAll()">Expand</button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="collapseAll()">Collapse</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="sections"></div>

  <div class="empty-state" id="empty-state">
    <h3>No matches.</h3>
    <p>Try a different keyword or clear the filter.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="wave-divider">~ ~ ~</div>

  <div class="summary-card">
    <h2>Export your <em>workbook</em></h2>
    <p>All decisions are tagged by section and question ID for clean hand-off to ops, cleaning teams, and guest comms.</p>
    <div class="summary-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num" id="stat-answered">0</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Resolved</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num" id="stat-total">0</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total Questions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num" id="stat-sections">0</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Sections</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num" id="stat-percent">0%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Complete</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-light" onclick="exportMarkdown()">↓ Markdown</button>
      <button class="btn btn-light" onclick="exportJSON()">↓ JSON</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="copyToClipboard()">⎘ Copy all</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="resetAll()">↻ Reset</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script>
const sections = [
  // ========== PROPERTY-SPECIFIC ==========
  {
    tag: "Property 01 · Sunnyside", theme: "property", marker: "I",
    title: "Beachfront Escape — Quiet Retreat On The Beach",
    questions: [
      { id: "P1.1", text: "Confirm max occupancy enforcement for this unit (8 guests): what happens if booking requests exceed this?" },
      { id: "P1.2", text: "How many vehicles/parking spots are allowed at this specific property?" },
      { id: "P1.3", text: "Are early check-in or late check-out ever allowed at this property despite posted rules?" },
      { id: "P1.4", text: "Are complimentary beach chairs/umbrella guaranteed here, and who sets them up?" },
      { id: "P1.5", text: "What should be communicated about private beach access and stair/steep-step expectations?" },
      { id: "P1.6", text: "What is the process if nearby construction impacts beach access during a stay?" },
      { id: "P1.7", text: "What property-specific cleaning QA checks should be completed before check-in (e.g., floor mop verification)?" },
      { id: "P1.8", text: "What are this property's smoking/vaping enforcement steps and fee amounts?" }
    ]
  },
  {
    tag: "Property 02 · Mistral", theme: "property", marker: "II",
    title: "Mistral 7 — Beachfront Condo with Ocean Views",
    questions: [
      { id: "P2.1", text: "Amenity lists '24-hour checkin' but house rules show fixed check-in: what is the official guest-facing policy?" },
      { id: "P2.2", text: "Sleeping setup says 5 guests / 1 bed: what exact sleeping layout should agents disclose?" },
      { id: "P2.3", text: "Is travel insurance recommendation mandatory in pre-stay messaging for this property?" },
      { id: "P2.4", text: "What are this property's exact parking limits and overflow guidance?" },
      { id: "P2.5", text: "What should be disclosed about steep stairs/private beach access for mobility-limited guests?" },
      { id: "P2.6", text: "Which nearby area recommendations should be auto-sent (Alys, Rosemary, Seaside, Big Chill)?" },
      { id: "P2.7", text: "What is the escalation path if guests report beach access obstruction (construction, erosion, closures)?" }
    ]
  },
  {
    tag: "Property 03 · Mistral Breeze", theme: "property", marker: "III",
    title: "Mistral Breeze 19 — Bohemian Beachfront Elegance",
    questions: [
      { id: "P3.1", text: "This is top-floor with lofted ceilings: what safety messaging is required for families with children?" },
      { id: "P3.2", text: "Sleeping setup says 8 guests / 2 beds: what exact bed + sleeper configuration should be communicated?" },
      { id: "P3.3", text: "Confirm no early check-in / no late check-out policy and any exception workflow." },
      { id: "P3.4", text: "What are this property's beach access/stair warnings and accessibility disclaimers?" },
      { id: "P3.5", text: "What property-specific quiet hours / HOA / noise expectations apply?" },
      { id: "P3.6", text: "What property-specific amenity replacement SLA applies if items are missing at check-in?" }
    ]
  },
  {
    tag: "Property 04 · Seamist", theme: "property", marker: "IV",
    title: "Seamist 7 — Beachfront on 30A",
    questions: [
      { id: "P4.1", text: "House rules mention a $150 check-in/out timing charge: who approves/assesses it and how is it documented?" },
      { id: "P4.2", text: "No smoking/vaping is explicit: what fee and evidence standard are required for enforcement?" },
      { id: "P4.3", text: "Address is shown publicly here: what are pre-booking vs post-booking address-sharing rules for this property?" },
      { id: "P4.4", text: "What are this property's specific checkout instructions beyond standard checklist?" },
      { id: "P4.5", text: "What are this property's exact parking limits and pre/post-stay parking rules?" },
      { id: "P4.6", text: "What specific communication is required when guests request early check-in at this property?" }
    ]
  },
  {
    tag: "Portfolio · Cross-Property", theme: "cross", marker: "★",
